                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6663" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1689</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8712 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化难为“易”，物尽其用：梅国良易货的破局之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Only action will sail us far: Mei Guoliang&#39;s way to break the situation of barter</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谌飞龙，陈松，谢萍，张卫俊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西华兴信息产业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易货平台；资源编排；企业转型；动态能力；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Barter platform; Resource arrangement; Enterprise transformation; Dynamic capability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">现代易货不仅是一种平台交易方式，更是一种资源编排的经营思想。在经济下行、媒体转型等剧烈变化的内外部复杂环境下，江西华兴信息公司董事长梅国良带领企业应对环境变局，调整企业发展方向，利用电商新技术赋能易货旧模式，推出媒体资源易货平台，巧妙盘活存量资源。本案例描述了江西华兴通过资源编排搭建新型易货贸易平台——“梅国良易货”的发展历程，引导学生思考动态环境下企业实施资源编排、资源整合，突破企业发展困境，实现企业转型发展。“梅国良易货”模式从最初“做供应链易货的开创者”，解决负债者无现金购买原材料等问题，发展到“用富余，换所需”，走向终端用户，利用市场机会创造社会价值，形成了资源从1到N的易货生态。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Modern barter is not only a way of platform trading, but also a management idea of resource arrangement. In the internal and external complex environment of drastic changes such as economic downturn and media transformation, Mei Guoliang, chairman of Jiangxi Huaxing Information Company, led the enterprise to cope with environmental changes, adjusted the development direction of the enterprise, and used new e-commerce technology to give new life to the old model of barter. Launch a barter platform for media resources to invigorate stock resources skillfully. This case describes the development process of Jiangxi Huaxing building a new barter trade platform &quot;Mei Guoliang barter&quot; through resource arrangement, guiding students to think about the implementation of resource arrangement and resource integration in the dynamic environment, so as to break through the predicament of enterprise development and realize the transformation and development of enterprises. The &quot;Mei Guoliang barter&quot; model has developed from &quot;being the pioneer of barter in the supply chain&quot; to solving the problem that debtors have no cash to buy raw materials, to &quot;using surplus for what they need&quot;, moving towards end-users, and making use of market opportunities to create social value. the formation of resources from 1 to N barter ecology.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">媒体易货的内涵；资源的概念及类型；资源编排的内涵及过程；资源编排的作用机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
